https://github.com/mui/base-ui/blob/e738519411acb250e189e50a5846336d66a3a0b7/packages/utils/src/detectBrowser.ts#L28 is the line in question. Changing this to:
```typescript
export const isMac =
  hasNavigator && platform?.toLowerCase().startsWith('mac') && !navigator.maxTouchPoints;
```
fixes the issue.

